    <section name="HttpDispatcher">
      <subsection name="Description">
        <p>HttpDispatcher is a straightforward interface that the LedgeServlet uses to delegate
        request processing to components. Note that dispatchers can be easily chained/multiplexed.
        </p>
      </subsection>
      
      <subsection name="Browse">
