          </ul>
        </p>
      </subsection>
      
      <subsection name="Implementations">
        <p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <p>HttpMethodDispatcher is a directs the requests to other dispatchers, depending on 
              HTTP method used in the request.</p>
              <p class="more"><a href="dispatcher/HttpMethodDispatcher.html">more</a></p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p>StaticHttpDispatcher returns hard coded responses for URLs matching a regular expression.
              Status code, content type and response body text can be configured.</p>
              <p class="more"><a href="dispatcher/StaticHttpDispatcher.html">more</a></p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </p>
      </subsection>
      
